Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞牆壁的… 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你再受傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,居然破壞牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己在做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為知道 所以不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這是… 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是世界真正的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,除了牆內 全都毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而宿命點不只是12隻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會無數地來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是這個世界 還是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要重複滿開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喪失身體功能也要繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天 連重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,開心的歲月的記憶也要失去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也要繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要再讓重要的朋友成為犧牲品了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不再成為勇者這一祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等… 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜 為什麼要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是大赦的勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦明明隱瞞了真相 把你當作道具使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈和勇者部的大家受傷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不想再看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友一次次受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,東… 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉那麼煩惱 那麼痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在旁邊眼睜睜看著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定能做到些什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是最好的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,現在要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友一次次受傷 失去重要之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.57,Text11a,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an2}警告\N因為勇者的精神狀態不穩定\N無法生成與神樹的靈力回路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎… 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要做到這個份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不知為何 突然想道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是這個家 還是勇者部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,都讓姐姐一身扛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而我總是又膽小 又弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,總是跟在姐姐後面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 其實我想和姐姐並肩前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別說並肩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺間 你不是站在我前面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,作為姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不能全靠妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒事了 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是我引以為豪的好妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 犬吠埼姐妹的女子力 就讓它們見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我們上 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒法變身！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這個朋友… 不合格…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友… 朋友沒什麼合格不合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你在因為東鄉的事情責備自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,該說像友奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想阻止東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界毀滅掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒法和大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可是… 現在的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不要作為大赦的勇者戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,今後要作為勇者部的一員戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓我們的勇者部被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我不想看到友奈的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再生後的傢伙湧出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,先要殲滅那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然後尋找東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有犧牲看來是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,諸行無常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂 現在開始才是重頭戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,遠的給我聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,近的就過來 也親眼看著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是贊州中學二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部部員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,三好夏凜的實力！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來 收下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其一！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,招呼要～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,打好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其二！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,盡量不放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,其三！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,睡好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,其四！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,煩惱要溝通！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,另一隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 傷得太淺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其五！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,車到山前多半～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有路！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,見識了嗎 勇者部的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 眼睛和耳朵好像都廢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是友奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 友奈 我的精彩表現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我都看到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好厲害 夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這種… 這種事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,本想去找東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我有話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我長久以來一直在接受勇者的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只有戰鬥是我的存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是個道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是… 多虧大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈的話 連東鄉的心意也能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能救東鄉的只有友奈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是最好的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到這個光景了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那應該明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再破壞牆壁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界 大赦的做法 勇者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是多麼悲慘的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要得到救贖 只有這個辦法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我作為部長 作為前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都要阻止你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,請原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,咬緊牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人停止進攻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 憑勇者的力量 沒法傷害神樹本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 帶這個去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能把神樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你想殺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就能把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不會迷惑了
